Cyberpunk style: A sleek modem router device sits on a desk in a dimly lit Singapore apartment at night, casting neon blue and magenta reflections. Through a rain-streaked window behind it, the glowing skyline of futuristic Singapore towers shimmer with holographic advertisements. Digital data streams visibly stutter and fragment around the router like glitching pixel waterfalls, some streams flowing smoothly while others dissolve into scattered voxels mid-air. A speed gauge hologram floats above the device, its needle wavering erratically between low and high. The scene captures frustration through visual metaphor—pristine technology surrounded by chaos, promise versus reality. Moody atmospheric lighting with deep shadows and vibrant accent colors typical of cyberpunk aesthetic.
